Invocation Name: jeremy's one liners
des:
Hear short, funny jokes and one-liners from this private collection.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Jeremy's one liners" or, "Alexa, read me a joke from Jeremy's one liners". To hear another, say "Another", or request a specific joke by number, like "read me joke number 42". Say, "repeat" if you didn't catch it the first time.

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
